data.title: Wass against Wass: Freestyle fun with the LaLiga Experience
data.meta_description: Valencia CF's Danish star Daniel Wass put himself to the test against against our latest signing, Wass Freestyle, in a day where players from VCF Femenino also got to enjoy the LaLiga Experience.

data.text:
The LaLiga Experience's latest two signings, who touched down in Spain from France and the United States, courtesy of beIN SPORTS France and beIN SPORTS USA, were invited to live it up for a day at Valencia CF's training complex, where they revelled in some truly unforgettable experiences.

After watching the men's first team get put through their paces on the training pitch, Wass Freestyle locked horns with Daniel Wass in an entertaining contest in which our guest showcased his considerable talents.

Meanwhile, former player Melissa Ortiz and beIN SPORTS USA commentator Ray Hudson put their knowledge of the women's game to the test in a quiz with Valencia's Natalia Gaitan and Monica Flores.

As if that wasn't enough excitement for one day, our visitors then got to explore the streets of Valencia as they took in the city's major attractions.
